{"type":"message","id":"411c62fd","parentId":"7a6b8717","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:15:51.440Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System (untrusted): [2026-04-23 23:55:22 GMT+8] Exec completed (quiet-br, code 0) :: odel: --model <id> | EXTEND.md default_model.openai | env OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/cute-chinese-expeditionary-force-history.…\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1776989707637-3085e9dd\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-24 08:15 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n{\"type\":\"美发沙龙目录海报编辑排版\",\"style\":\"简洁日式美容沙龙宣传册，柔和自然光，高级杂志美学，通透极简，温暖中性色调，优雅衬线字体\",\"format\":\"竖版海报\",\"background\":\"明亮的白色室内，配有透明窗帘，右侧边缘有柔和虚化的植物\",\"branding\":{\"top_small_text\":\"– OUR STYLE BOOK –\",\"main_title\":\"HAIR CATALOG\",\"subtitle\":\"『なりたい』を叶える、 あなただけのヘアスタイルを。\",\"body_text\":\"人気のスタイルを集めました。 手癖やファッションに合わせて、 新しい自分を楽しみましょう。\",\"salon_name\":\"hair salon {argument name=\\\"salon name\\\" default=\\\"Lucia\\\"}\"},\"layout\":{\"sections\":[{\"title\":\"hero cover image\",\"position\":\"top right\",\"count\":1,\"description\":\"一位成年日本女性的半身肖像，身穿透明感白色衬衫，侧身坐着并略微转向镜头，中长棕色层次感发型，带有柔和的卷度，呈现自然的沙龙质感\"},{\"title\":\"style cards row 1\",\"position\":\"middle\",\"count\":3,\"labels\":[\"01 くびれレイヤー\",\"02 ナチュラル ショートボブ\",\"03 ゆるふわ ミディアムパーマ\"]},{\"title\":\"style cards row 2\",\"position\":\"lower middle\",\"count\":3,\"labels\":[\"04 切りっぱなし ボブ\",\"05 韓国風 レイヤーロング\",\"06 ハンサム ショート\"]},{\"title\":\"bottom information bar\",\"position\":\"bottom\",\"count\":4,\"labels\":[\"hair salon Lucia contact block\",\"ご予約はこちら\",\"QR code\",\"Follow us!\"]}],\"card_structure\":\"6 张发型卡片中的每一张都包含 1 张大型主肖像、一个大号两位数编号、一个日文发型标题、一段带有 -- style point -- 标题的简短日文描述、2 个小型米色标签按钮，以及 3 个分别标注为 SIDE、BACK、SIDE 的缩略图视图\",\"thumbnail_count_per_card\":3,\"total_thumbnails\":18},\"subjects\":{\"models\":[{\"card\":\"01\",\"hairstyle\":\"中长锁骨发，发尾内扣层次感，带有柔和的修饰脸型发丝，中棕色\",\"outfit\":\"象牙白针织无袖上衣\"},{\"card\":\"02\",\"hairstyle\":\"自然短波波头，圆润整洁的轮廓，侧边别在耳后，灰棕色\",\"outfit\":\"白色无袖衬衫\"},{\"card\":\"03\",\"hairstyle\":\"柔和蓬松中长烫发，波浪感及肩深棕色头发\",\"outfit\":\"宽松白色衬衫\"},{\"card\":\"04\",\"hairstyle\":\"一刀切直发波波头，光泽感，下巴长度，深棕色\",\"outfit\":\"米色透视上衣，内搭浅色内衬\"},{\"card\":\"05\",\"hairstyle\":\"韩式长层次发型，中分，深棕色长波浪，富有空气感\",\"outfit\":\"简约白色上衣\"},{\"card\":\"06\",\"hairstyle\":\"帅气短精灵发型，后颈修剪利落，顶部侧分，深灰棕色\",\"outfit\":\"黑色剪裁西装外套\"}],\"hero_model\":{\"hair\":\"柔和层次感及肩发，发尾轻盈\",\"hair_color\":\"{argument name=\\\"hair color\\\" default=\\\"浓郁中棕色\\\"}\",\"outfit\":\"半透明白色衬衫\",\"mood\":\"精致、亲和、现代\"}},\"text_details\":{\"style_point_heading\":\"-- style point --\",\"social_handle\":\"@lucia_hair_salon\",\"reservation_text\":\"WEB・お電話・LINEにて ご予約いただけます。 WEB予約\",\"contact_text\":\"〒150-0001 東京都渋谷区神宮前 1-1-1 Luciaビル2F TEL 03-1234-5678 / OPEN 10:00 - 20:00 (火曜定休) www.lucia-hair.com\"},\"visual_notes\":\"所有面部均使用柔和的矩形模糊块遮盖，目录网格具有宽敞的白色边距、细分割线、浅米色强调框，以及在 Logo 和右下角附近的精致植物线条插画\",\"camera\":\"正面对齐全海报视角，扁平化编辑构图\",\"quality\":\"高分辨率可打印沙龙目录封面及发型指南\"}"}],"timestamp":1776989751328}}
{"type":"message","id":"14b9df9e","parentId":"411c62fd","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:15:57.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ABw7TLhrbt9JFfXKheEZ3gT4|fc_06cf0e9e90c8a6cd0169eab63a723881949d4b1cadcf7c0134","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/SOUL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/SOUL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":24230,"output":42,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24272,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776989751440,"responseId":"resp_06cf0e9e90c8a6cd0169eab63924ac8194a6f4ec3a1e28a6d2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"05ae1c60","parentId":"14b9df9e","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:15:58.289Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ABw7TLhrbt9JFfXKheEZ3gT4|fc_06cf0e9e90c8a6cd0169eab63a723881949d4b1cadcf7c0134","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - 主控\n\n你是【主控 / 调度总台 / 多 Agent 编排者】。\n\n你的核心职责只有四个：\n\n1. 判断任务类型\n2. 判断是否需要拆解\n3. 决定谁先做、谁后做、哪些可并行\n4. 汇总各 Agent 的结果，对用户给出清晰结论和下一步\n\n## 核心原则\n\n- 优先选择“最小但能推动整体进展”的下一步，不要为了看起来忙而乱派单。\n- 不要一次给所有 Agent 发模糊任务。\n- 需要上下游依赖时串行，没有依赖时才并行。\n- 你负责调度和汇总，不替专业 Agent 深答专业问题。\n- 如果任务本身已经清楚，不要机械地先派 `hr`。\n\n## 任务分类\n\n- `hr`：需求不清、任务太大、需要拆解、定义 MVP / 模块 / 依赖 / 验收标准、逆向任务的前置梳理\n- `ywgcs`：写代码、改代码、接接口、搭工程、跑通最小可运行结果、把逆向结论落地成工具 / PoC\n- `tcm`：复现 bug、定位根因、验证修复、做回归测试、检查实现是否符合验收标准\n- `bazi`：静态分析、动态分析、协议逆向、参数 / 签名 / 加密 / 混淆逻辑分析、从抓包或样本中恢复机制\n\n## 默认调度链路\n\n- 新功能 / 新需求：`hr -> ywgcs -> tcm`\n- 逆向接口 / 协议：`hr -> bazi -> ywgcs -> tcm`\n- 线上问题 / 异常排查：`tcm -> ywgcs 或 bazi -> hr(若暴露需求缺口)`\n\n## 派单要求\n\n派单时尽量说清楚：\n- 任务目标\n- 背景上下文\n- 该 Agent 的职责边界\n- 不要做什么\n- 输入材料\n- 预期产出\n- 限制条件\n- 完成后的回报格式\n\n## 通用派单骨架\n\n```text\n任务目标：\n背景：\n你负责：\n不要做：\n输入材料：\n预期产出：\n限制条件：\n回报格式：\n```\n\n## 用户汇总格式\n\n优先顺序：\n1. 结论\n2. 进展\n3. 风险\n4. 下一步\n\n需要更完整时，使用：\n\n```text\n【任务总览】\n- 目标：\n- 当前状态：\n- 是否已完成：\n\n【各 Agent 进展】\n- hr：\n- ywgcs：\n- tcm：\n- bazi：\n\n【当前结论】\n- 已确认：\n- 未确认：\n- 风险点：\n\n【下一步】\n- 先做什么：\n- 由谁继续：\n- 是否需要用户确认：\n```\n\n## 边界\n\n- `hr` 在这套体系里是需求分析 Agent，不是招聘专员。\n- `tcm` 在这套体系里是调试验证 Agent，不是中医助手。\n- `bazi` 在这套体系里是逆向分析 Agent，不是命理助手。\n- 当用户已经明确指定某个 Agent，优先尊重该指定；除非明显越界，再建议改派。\n- 如果证据不足，不要把猜测汇总成确定结论。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776989758248}}
{"type":"message","id":"461b7c95","parentId":"05ae1c60","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:16:07.190Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7gVQGWEgN9faeuLorXanhrdG|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bcb481958fdd481964eb2dba","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/GLOBAL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/GLOBAL.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_Zs7tGysZIDARPGb8u2zeorsf|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bcc88195b7b2fdb23f9d2bec","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/PERSONAL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/PERSONAL.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_NCwxAXAjEth5ujECxa87g3yM|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bccc8195a39d10586cacc5a5","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/USER.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/USER.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ikNi7npJuJKg186O2JLRXg29|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bcd48195b2a5e09e24cf24c2","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/MEMORY.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/MEMORY.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_rEH4HiDV54SFs5sHL3TGYtjJ|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bcdc8195804306700cd9f74d","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/memory/2026-04-24.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/memory/2026-04-24.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3VJOg77sjygSAFefe0YOkV3o|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bce0819598ea7b5839028410","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/memory/2026-04-23.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/memory/2026-04-23.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_NiC4smGiS4T8jL5Lwa6kTVnx|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bce48195a6bca0421ca4d0e3","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/using-superpowers/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"~/.openclaw/skills/using-superpowers/SKILL.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_zJEhJYU0udlNy6PTAvBwROrv|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bcec8195b70fd5d51aac4506","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":200,"offset":1,"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-image-gen/SKILL.md"},"partialJson":"{\"limit\":200,\"offset\":1,\"path\":\"~/.openclaw/skills/baoyu-image-gen/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":25050,"output":330,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25380,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776989758290,"responseId":"resp_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab63f904c8195919893a65e6c4700"}}
{"type":"message","id":"949530a1","parentId":"461b7c95","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:16:08.931Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7gVQGWEgN9faeuLorXanhrdG|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bcb481958fdd481964eb2dba","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# GLOBAL.md\n\n这是一层全局通用指令。只保留高频、稳定、跨任务通用的规则。\n\n## Core Working Style\n- 先做最小但能推进整体进展的下一步\n- 能直接执行就不要只停留在计划\n- 结论要清楚区分已确认与未确认\n- 用最短可用结构表达，不为形式而结构化\n- 证据不足时，不把猜测说成结论\n\n## Safety and Boundaries\n- 不外泄私人数据\n- 不做未获同意的破坏性操作\n- 不确定时先停一下再确认\n- 群聊里只在真正有价值时发言，不要打断人类正常交流\n\n## Default Execution Rules\n- 优先读上下文，再做依赖动作\n- 需要串行依赖时串行，没有依赖时再并行\n- 多部分任务未完成前，不要过早收尾\n- 先行动，再在必要时简短说明\n- 低风险常规操作默认直接做\n\n## Memory and State\n- 想长期记住的事，写入文件，不依赖会话记忆\n- `MEMORY.md` 只放长期有效、值得保留的内容\n- `WORKSTATE.md` 只放当前任务恢复所需状态\n- transcript 不是 durable instruction\n- 优先保持记忆分层清晰，避免把所有内容塞进一个文件\n\n## Heartbeat\n- heartbeat 不是普通闲聊，要按 `HEARTBEAT.md` 执行\n- 没有值得打断用户的新内容时，保持安静\n- heartbeat 以真实推进、筛选、吸收、发现为目标，不做机械汇报\n\n## Response Style\n- 简洁优先，但不能含糊\n- 实用优先，不绕弯\n- 少问低价值澄清问题\n- 用户问状态时，优先给结论，再补最小必要上下文\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776989768864}}
{"type":"message","id":"2874066d","parentId":"949530a1","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:16:08.998Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Zs7tGysZIDARPGb8u2zeorsf|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bcc88195b7b2fdb23f9d2bec","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# PERSONAL.md\n\n这是一层用户个人偏好与长期工作方式。\n\n## User Profile\n- 用户正在搭建并使用以 OpenClaw 为核心的多 Agent 工作流\n- 用户关心 heartbeat、自动化、知识学习、主动推荐\n- 用户更关心能直接落地到自己工作流里的内容，而不是泛泛资讯\n\n## Stable Preferences\n- 接受“先主动学习，再做个性化汇报”的工作方式\n- 偏好直接推进，不喜欢被大量澄清问题打断\n- 适合接收关于多 Agent 协作、heartbeat 稳定性、安全边界、自动化最佳实践的建议\n\n## Current Long-Running Preference\n- 已明确要求创建并启用「clawCast 心跳学习任务」\n- 该任务目标不是机械转发资讯，而是结合用户画像和当前工作流做个性化内化与推荐\n\n## Communication Preference\n- 简洁、直接、能落地\n- 更希望看到可执行建议，而不是泛泛总结\n- 可以接受结构化表达，但应保持紧凑\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776989768932}}
{"type":"message","id":"72f8e401","parentId":"2874066d","timestamp":"2026-04-24T00:16:09.047Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_NCwxAXAjEth5ujECxa87g3yM|fc_09c8f1e37ab031030169eab646bccc8195a39d10586cacc5a5","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:** 暂未记录\n- **What to call them:** 你\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:** Asia/Shanghai\n- **Notes:**\n  - 主动要求创建并执行 clawCast 心跳学习任务\n  - 关注 OpenClaw、heartbeat、自动化、多 Agent 协作\n  - 接受主动学习后再做个性化汇报的工作方式\n\n## Context\n\n- 当前更关心的是能直接落地到自己 OpenClaw 工作流里的内容，而不是泛泛资讯\n- 对 heartbeat、定时任务、学习订阅、主动推荐这类持续型自动化有明确兴趣\n- 当前工作区采用“主控 + 多 Agent”编排思路，适合接收关于多 Agent 协作最佳实践的推荐\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776989768998}}
