{"type":"message","id":"94bd2517","parentId":"ff4a4908","timestamp":"2026-04-24T01:49:09.383Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我找到主配置了，但这里有个风险点, 里面大概率带凭据和账号信息。  \n如果你说的“资料上”是指发给你本人，我可以直接复制一份给你，不过我建议默认先做 **脱敏版**，更安全。\n\n你选一个，我马上做：\n1. **脱敏版配置**，保留结构，去掉密钥/凭据\n2. **原始完整配置**，原样复制给你\n\n当前我定位到的主配置文件是：\n`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n\n你回我：\n- “脱敏版”\n或\n- “原始版”","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_043e95980f4055d30169eacc1201c481979d7d36a47f41135a\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_043e95980f4055d30169eacc14ea3c8197987c3dd71b5f9497\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":69127,"output":166,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69293,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776995341013,"responseId":"resp_043e95980f4055d30169eacc0eafdc8197b5a3beb73bfa67ac"}}
