{"type":"message","id":"f6700b13","parentId":"fe105b75","timestamp":"2026-04-24T02:10:19.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我这边已经帮你定位到了 OpenClaw 的主配置文件：\n\n- 主配置：`/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/openclaw.json`\n\n另外我也顺手扫到了一批相关配置/状态文件，比如：\n- 微信插件账号：`.openclaw/openclaw-weixin/accounts/...`\n- 定时任务：`.openclaw/cron/jobs.json`\n- 设备身份：`.openclaw/identity/device.json`\n- 配对/凭据：`.openclaw/credentials/...`\n\n不过这些里很多都可能带敏感信息，所以我刚才先停在这一步，没有直接发。\n\n你只要回我一个词，我就继续：\n- **脱敏版**，我复制一份安全版给你\n- **原始版**，我原样复制给你","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_043e95980f4055d30169ead0fda5688197b24c76b678124f51\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":69420,"output":186,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69606,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776996595079,"responseId":"resp_043e95980f4055d30169ead0fb6b208197b49773ec4e004852"}}
