{"type":"message","id":"e79f1614","parentId":"e5159b9c","timestamp":"2026-04-24T10:31:17.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"能装，我已经确认这不是 App 安装包，而是一个 **OpenClaw 技能包**，名字叫：\n\n- `gpt-image-generator`\n\n里面有这些文件：\n- `SKILL.md`\n- `scripts/generate_image.py`\n- `scripts/generate_image_edit.py`\n- `.env`\n- `references/env.example`\n\n不过还差最后一步配置，这个技能需要你自己的接口参数：\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL`\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY`\n\n我建议这样装，最稳：\n\n1. 我把它安装到  \n   `~/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator`\n2. 再把 `.env` 配好\n3. 然后帮你跑一次验证\n\n现在卡点只有一个：\n**你要不要让我直接安装，但先保留它自带 `.env` 原样不改？**\n\n你回我一句：\n- **直接安装**\n或\n- **安装并帮我配置**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_043e95980f4055d30169eb4671a2748197962e1b8684ec5d5f\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"text","text":"","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_043e95980f4055d30169eb4675631481978ff53fd4c05306b5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":101171,"output":214,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101385,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777026668637,"responseId":"resp_043e95980f4055d30169eb466e1b5481978753aa53a064024b"}}
