{"type":"message","id":"0d9fc8d4","parentId":"cc584324","timestamp":"2026-04-24T10:32:35.220Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"装好了。\n\n安装位置：\n- `/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/home/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator`\n\n已放进去的文件有：\n- `.env`\n- `SKILL.md`\n- `references/env.example`\n- `scripts/generate_image.py`\n- `scripts/generate_image_edit.py`\n\n下一步如果你要让它真能用，还需要配这两个环境变量：\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL`\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY`\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以继续帮你：\n- 检查 `.env` 现在写了什么\n- 帮你补配置\n- 直接跑一次测试生成","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_043e95980f4055d30169eb46c0918c8197bac3a61dcf9c27d6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":101951,"output":148,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":102099,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777026748266,"responseId":"resp_043e95980f4055d30169eb46bde6188197a45989b94d086f59"}}
