{"type":"message","id":"98f8a25f","parentId":"275ffd6c","timestamp":"2026-04-24T10:35:42.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我试了，已经定位到阻塞点了。\n\n结果：\n- 技能脚本能正常启动\n- `.env` 也读到了\n- 但测试生成失败，接口返回 **401**\n\n当前报错：\n- `HTTP_ERROR 401 {\"error\":\"Invalid API key\"}`\n\n也就是说，不是安装坏了，而是 **现在这个 `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY` 无效**。\n\n你这个技能当前配置是：\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8317/v1/responses`\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY=[REDACTED]`\n\n下一步最直接的是二选一：\n1. 你给我一个可用的新 `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY`\n2. 或者我帮你检查本机这个 `8317` 接口到底要求什么 key / 有没有换过配置\n\n如果你愿意，我下一步可以直接帮你继续查本机接口配置。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_043e95980f4055d30169eb477b241c8197b37481e099a2998e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":104116,"output":206,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104322,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777026935247,"responseId":"resp_043e95980f4055d30169eb4778c44c81978cffc9705ca00123"}}
